# ГўвЂќв‚¬ГўвЂќв‚¬ STEP 4b: Affiliate vanity links Гўв‚¬вЂќ proxy to the Render backend ГўвЂќв‚¬
#
# /ref/:slug is an Express route on Render, not a Netlify page.
# Without this rule, uyehtech.com/ref/somecreator 404s on Netlify Гўв‚¬вЂќ
# it never reaches the backend at all.
#
# 301 = simple redirect: browser briefly shows the Render domain, then
# Render's own res.redirect() bounces it again to /marketplace/?ref=CODE
# on uyehtech.com. Two hops, but simple and reliable.
#
# If you'd rather the address bar never shows the Render domain, change
# 301 to 200 to make Netlify reverse-proxy it instead (keeps uyehtech.com
# in the bar throughout) Гўв‚¬вЂќ test this option before relying on it, proxy
# behavior with upstream redirects can be inconsistent across Netlify plans.

/ref/*            https://uyehtechbackend.onrender.com/ref/:splat   301

